verbose_text: Another study utilized a 15-mer-AHSRGDTFQTSSGCG peptide of KSHV-gB and demonstrated that this peptide mediated the human fibrosarcoma HT1080 cell adhesion which was blocked by alphaVbeta3 and alphaVbeta5 antibodies while peptide bound beads detected only alphaVbeta3 integrin.
evidence: cell adhesion which was blocked by alphaVbeta3 and alphaVbeta5 antibodies
